ok&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=AnimeOnDVD%3A+%22Serial+Experiments+Lain+Vol.+%231%22+Review&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Beveridge&amp;rft.aufirst=Chris&amp;rft.au=Beveridge%2C+Chris&amp;rft.date=1999-07-13&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.animeondvd.com%2Freviews2%2Fdisc_reviews%2F687.php&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Serial_Experiments_Lain"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>, <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFSouthworth">Southworth, Wayne. <a href="http://www.thespinningimage.co.uk/cultfilms/displaycultfilm.asp?reviewid=872&amp;aff=13" class="external text" title="http://www.thespinningimage.co.uk/cultfilms/displaycultfilm.asp?reviewid=872&amp;aff=13" rel="nofollow">"The Spinning Image: "Serial Experiments Lain Volume 4: Reset" Review"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.thespinningimage.co.uk/cultfilms/displaycultfilm.asp?reviewid=872&amp;aff=13" class="external free" title="http://www.thespinningimage.co.uk/cultfilms/displaycultfilm.asp?reviewid=872&amp;aff=13" rel="nofollow">http://www.thespinningimage.co.uk/cultfilms/displaycultfilm.asp?reviewid=872&amp;aff=13</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2006-09-16</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+Spinning+Image%3A+%22Serial+Experiments+Lain+Volume+4%3A+Reset%22+Review&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Southworth&amp;rft.aufirst=Wayne&amp;rft.au=Southworth%2C+Wayne&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thespinningimage.co.uk%2Fcultfilms%2Fdisplaycultfilm.asp%3Freviewid%3D872%26aff%3D13&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Serial_Experiments_Lain"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
